      <strong>Type:</strong> Mid-sized Phoenix local investor.<br />
      <strong>Operating in Phoenix:</strong> Yes; established presence.<br />
      <strong>Typical offer:</strong> 70-80% ARV.<br />
      <strong>Typical close:</strong> 14-30 days.<br />
      <strong>Best for:</strong> Sellers who want a personalized local-investor experience with established brand presence. Properties in the standard-condition to mild-distress range.
    </p>
    <p>
